author: Danny Schwartz
title: Future Reveals "FUTURE" Album Tracklist
text:
Home > Music > Future Reveals "FUTURE" Album Tracklist Future Reveals "FUTURE" Album Tracklist 0 0 Posted by Danny Schwartz , Feb 15, 2017 at 06:04pm Future's self-titled album arrives this Friday. 
Yesterday, Future announced that he will be releasing a self-titled album on Friday, February 17 and going on tour with Migos , Tory Lanez and Kodak Black this spring. The FUTURE tracklist has now been revealed on iTunes : 
1 Rent Money 
14 Massage In My Room 
15 Flip 
16 When I Was Broke 
17 Feds Did a Sweep
